            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botan Garden ¶ 15. Aug. 1864. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter dated 3. Aug, ¶  which with its enclosures reached me two days ago. Altho' her Majestys Go...</supplied>
